  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a paella pan over medium heat.",
    "Sauté onion and garlic until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add saffron-infused water and chicken broth, then bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add asparagus, stirring gently to coat in the liquid.",
    "Simmer for 8-10 minutes until asparagus is tender but still crisp-tender.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
